title: Game Review Episode 1 - Twilight Struggle
itunes:author: The History of the Cold War Podcast
itunes:summary:
Join us for our Game Review of the popular Cold War board and video game Twilight Struggle.  Jeff gives his opinions on the game play, challenge level, and how faithful it is to actual Cold War history.
